com.pos.device.emv

Class TerminalMckConfigure

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pos.device.emv.TerminalMckConfigure

  • public class TerminalMckConfigure
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the terminal MCK（Multi-Configuration Kernel）configuration of EMV core.

    Note:

    1: Support; 0 :No Support

    Supported default if you don't set properity.

    Author：Paddy Email：pjpsmile@126.com 2016/3/28 10:23
